                                         Table "public.invoices"
     Column      |           Type           | Collation | Nullable |               Default                
-----------------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+--------------------------------------
 id              | integer                  |           | not null | nextval('invoices_id_seq'::regclass)
 invoice_number  | text                     |           | not null | 
 order_id        | integer                  |           |          | 
 user_id         | uuid                     |           |          | 
 customer_name   | text                     |           | not null | 
 customer_email  | text                     |           | not null | 
 customer_phone  | text                     |           |          | 
 billing_street  | text                     |           | not null | 
 billing_street2 | text                     |           |          | 
 billing_city    | text                     |           | not null | 
 billing_state   | text                     |           | not null | 
 billing_zip     | text                     |           | not null | 
 billing_country | text                     |           | not null | 'United States'::text
 subtotal        | numeric(12,2)            |           | not null | 
 tax             | numeric(12,2)            |           | not null | 0
 shipping_fee    | numeric(12,2)            |           | not null | 0
 total           | numeric(12,2)            |           | not null | 
 amount_paid     | numeric(12,2)            |           | not null | 0
 balance_due     | numeric(12,2)            |           | not null | 
 status          | invoice_status           |           | not null | 'draft'::invoice_status
 issue_date      | date                     |           | not null | CURRENT_DATE
 due_date        | date                     |           | not null | 
 paid_date       | date                     |           |          | 
 notes           | text                     |           |          | 
 created_at      | timestamp with time zone |           | not null | now()
 updated_at      | timestamp with time zone |           | not null | now()
Indexes:
    "invoices_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "idx_invoices_due_date" btree (due_date)
    "idx_invoices_order_id" btree (order_id)
    "idx_invoices_status" btree (status)
    "idx_invoices_user_id" btree (user_id)
    "invoices_invoice_number_key" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (invoice_number)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "invoices_order_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (order_id) REFERENCES orders(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
    "invoices_user_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
Referenced by:
    TABLE "invoice_items" CONSTRAINT "invoice_items_invoice_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (invoice_id) REFERENCES invoices(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
Triggers:
    update_invoices_updated_at BEFORE UPDATE ON invoices FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_updated_at_column()

